Unitron/Anubis/Hades:

::Anubis twirls through the air, having moved to the right, the shot form 
Rampage nailing him in the shoulder, Anubis passing out from pain::

::Hades saw this, running forward and bringing the butt of his laser rifle at 
Inferno's chin::

::Unitron watched, firing off two laser bolts at Rampage's left knee, then 
speaking into his com, a missile launcher emerged from the side of the ship, 
firing a missile at both Rampage, and Inferno::
